	Cruz fat wedding    
	 Los Angeles, March 13 (PTI): Actress Penelope Cruz is reportedly planning a big fat Spanish wedding with actor Javier Bardem and has asked rock legend Mick Jaggers girlfriend to design her gown.       
	Cruz, who has been dating her Vicky Christina Barcelona co-star since 2007, has called on LWren Scott, Utah-born fashion queen, to design a fairytale dress for her, reports In Touch Weekly. Penelope is working closely with LWren. Her dress will be one-of-a-kind and be accented with real pearls, said a source.    
	Bruni affair    
	 London (PTI): After reports of President Nicolas Sarkozy and First Lady Carla Bruni cheating on each other, the former supermodel is seen having an affair in a cheeky episode of The Simpsons. In the episode, Bruni has a fling with Homers workmate Carl Carlson when he visits Paris, reports The Sun. It was made before the allegations about Carla surfaced, a source said.                                                                                                                                                       
